    "name": "model",
    "purpose": "Owns the agent model backend abstraction. backend.rs defines the public ModelBackend trait, the crate-internal ModelBackendImpl trait bridged to ModelBackend by a blanket impl that delegates request to send, and the ModelRequest/ModelResponse request and response shapes; backend_deepseek.rs implements DeepseekBackend as a config-driven streaming Deepseek chat-completions backend over reqwest with SSE parsing and a user-role single-message payload that preserves request.prompt as content; error.rs defines ModelBackendError with From conversions for io, serde_json, and reqwest errors plus a Display impl. mod.rs is namespace and re-export wiring only.",
